♪Light still shines♪

3
00:00:28,093 --> 00:00:32,029
♪Tragedy and joy are sung♪

4
00:00:33,277 --> 00:00:35,177
♪But tricks can't be dodged♪

5
00:00:35,325 --> 00:00:38,013
♪Seek for purity in a chaotic world♪

6
00:00:38,269 --> 00:00:42,897
♪Anger and sorrow unfold♪

7
00:00:43,453 --> 00:00:45,376
♪Whether it's fate or love♪

8
00:00:45,661 --> 00:00:48,120
♪Is it meant to be or just chance♪

9
00:00:48,509 --> 00:00:52,745
♪In the haze, the truth emerges♪

10
00:00:53,021 --> 00:00:57,784
♪Clouds above, dust below♪

11
